# cyfs://$zone_id/home/

User personal data directory. Each user has their own sub-directory:

- $username/                   : user home, usually read-only or inaccessible to apps
- $username/.local/share/$appid/ : app persistent data, deleted on app uninstall (user can opt to keep)
- $username/shared/            : user-level shared data, typically read-only

This data is NOT deleted on system uninstall.
